    • City of Canada Bay Council meetings

    Council meeting dates are adopted each year by resolution of Council. Council confirmed the dates for 2024 at the meeting on Tuesday, 21 November 2023.  

    At 19 March 2024, Council meeting a resolution was passed to change the 19 November 2024 meeting to 12 November 2024. 

    Council Meeting Dates as follows:

    Tuesday, 20 February
    Tuesday, 19 March
    Tuesday, 16 April
    Tuesday, 21 May
    Tuesday, 18 June
    Tuesday, 16 July
    Tuesday, 20 August
    Tuesday, 15 October
    Tuesday, 12 November
    Tuesday, 3 December

    Generally, Council meets on the third Tuesday of the month (with the exception of January). However, there may be times when meetings will need to be rescheduled.

    Meetings are held at the Canada Bay Civic Centre, 1A Marlborough Street, Drummoyne at 6pm, with the exception of Extraordinary Meetings, which may be held in an emergency. 

    Code of Meeting Practice

    The Council has a Code of Meeting Practice which can be accessed here. Council also has a Remote Meeting Supplement to form part of its Code of Meeting Practice. This can be accessed here - it outlines methods of conducting remotely held online Council and Committee meetings. 

    Request to address Council

    If you would like to address a Council meeting, the item must be on the Agenda and you will need to complete and return Council’s Request to Address Council Meeting application form by 3pm on the day of the meeting. This will then be sent to the Council Meeting Submissions inbox.

    The public will be able to view a live stream of each meeting in the usual way, via a livestream on our Facebook Page at 6pm the evening of the Council meeting.

    Archived recordings of the meetings will continue to be made available on our Accessing agendas/minutes section below.

    Agendas

    Council agendas are available on the Council’s website from the Thursday before each meeting.

    Minutes

    Minutes are available once confirmed by Council.

    Accessing agendas/minutes

    Please scroll down to access Agendas/Minutes for recent Council Meetings. Click here to access minutes of meetings prior to 2018. Please note you will need to use the search feature and filter by date.
